BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:event_313449224@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260308T211700Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260312T114500
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260312T124500
SUMMARY:Experience Public Speaking with the NRV Lunch Bunch - Hybrid Meeti
 ng
DESCRIPTION:Southwest VA Toastmasters of Roanoke/Blacksburg/Rocky Mount\nJ
 oin us for an interactive meeting hosted by the Southwest VA Toastmasters 
 of the NRV Lunch Bunch. This event is perfect for anyone looking to conque
 r their fear of public speaking\, enhance their communication skills\, and
  boost their confidence. You'll learn valuable techniques for impromptu sp
 eaking\, effective presentations\, and self-empowerment through engaging a
 ctivities and supportive feedback from experienced Toastmasters. Whether y
 ou're a novice or seasoned speaker\, this club will provide a safe space t
 o practice and develop your public speaking skills in a friendly and encou
 raging environment. Don't miss this opportunity to unleash your full poten
 tial and become a more confident communicator! You can also join us virtua
 lly on Zoom. Contact us for the link at http://bit.ly/4gq5xfe.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/southwest-va-toastmasters-meetup-grou
 p/events/313449224/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260220T184149Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260220T184149Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:event_313449225@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260308T211700Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260312T120000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260312T130000
SUMMARY:Mastering Public Speaking with the Franklin County Toastmasters(Ro
 cky Mount\, VA)
DESCRIPTION:Southwest VA Toastmasters of Roanoke/Blacksburg/Rocky Mount\nJ
 oin us in Southwest VA at the Franklin County Toastmasters for a meeting f
 ocused on mastering public speaking and communication in general. Whether 
 you're a seasoned Toastmaster or looking to improve your communication ski
 lls\, this workshop is designed to help you think on your feet and deliver
  compelling speeches on the spot. Led by experienced Toastmasters\, you'll
  learn techniques to boost your confidence\, improve your impromptu speaki
 ng abilities\, and captivate any audience. Don't miss this opportunity to 
 enhance your communication skills in a supportive and interactive environm
 ent. Let's conquer the fear of public speaking together and become confide
 nt communicators!\n\nFor more information\, contact the club at http://bit
 .ly/3VNwkbz.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/southwest-va-toastmasters-meetup-grou
 p/events/313449225/
